highlights.text: “171” by lascar is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs France, up 17 spots at #46.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs France. “Briller - Golden - version française” is the highest at #14.
“Nope your too late i already died” by wifiskeleton and i wanna be a jack-o-lantern has been on Viral Songs France the longest, at 133 days straight.
“What a Difference a Day Makes (from the Netflix Limited Series "Black Rabbit")” by RAYE is the highest new entry on Viral Songs France at #87.
